{"tid":1632072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日全輸","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:49.000Z","uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0280408dab27cd9746066c3af25593b43e5a862d","tid":1632072,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177844dd4d3bb9f4e5f9e451f1cd6c1c690940fa","tid":1632072,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"be33848d2143d89d9a85a418aa5dee12f3f5c5f4","tid":1632072,"uid":170808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0280408dab27cd9746066c3af25593b43e5a862d","tid":1632072,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"你賭馬？"},{"pid":"15db13c0f23a6551ff4b898d5b91ca83f24ed7af","tid":1632072,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be33848d2143d89d9a85a418aa5dee12f3f5c5f4","tid":1632072,"uid":170808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0280408dab27cd9746066c3af25593b43e5a862d","tid":1632072,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"你賭馬？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"的士咁撞斷腳唔係輸係咩"},{"pid":"b73ede64287ba925da64326faf6dd50590f8191e","tid":1632072,"uid":287211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"越亂 証明林鄭越有用去平亂<br />\n<br />\n越亂就想美國唔好企我們呢到 影響法案辣度<br />\n<br />\n我們拉長嚟玩 條臭西趁越亂 乘機出師有名推其他法<br />\n<br />\n冚家產 蒙面法之後 佢點到會贏<br />\n<br />\n1） 更亂 可推其他乜撚緊急法 96小時乜春之類法<br />\n<br />\n2） 平靜咗 証明條蒙面法係有用 回復少少秩序之類<br />\n<br />\n所以條臭西點都贏<br />\n<br />\n但我地冷靜下先 亂同平靜D的結果 邊個畫面達到制裁目標容易些？ 當然我假設大家想班狗賊同我們欖炒! 記得謝蛇移民case? 呢D先至係我哋要的清算目標！<br />\n<br />\n所以 忍一下先 唔好比條臭西帶到我哋！<br />\n<br />\n我不是叫大家晤搞 只是拉長嚟玩 有先後次序<br />\n<br />\n我哋翻新黨鐵計劃延遲二三星期 黨鐡仲會係到 所以押後一下！ 大家想想！"},{"pid":"8cee3f1326a5ae52e268ca44853832f9caf5cef8","tid":1632072,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15db13c0f23a6551ff4b898d5b91ca83f24ed7af","tid":1632072,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be33848d2143d89d9a85a418aa5dee12f3f5c5f4","tid":1632072,"uid":170808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0280408dab27cd9746066c3af25593b43e5a862d","tid":1632072,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"你賭馬？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"的士咁撞斷腳唔係輸係咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:49.000Z","msg":"所以要諗應付呢類事件既對策"}]}